%%{init: {"sequence": {"actorMargin": 50, "messageAlign": "left"}, "themeVariables": {"fontFamily": "Inter, system-ui, sans-serif"}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor subject as Data subject
    participant api as Your Agent / API
    participant orch as Erasure<br/>Orchestrator
    participant prov as Provenance<br/>Index
    participant adp as Adapters<br/>(graph · vector · log)
    participant sign as Receipt<br/>Signer
    participant reg as Regulator<br/>(or auditor)

    subject->>api: "Erase everything you know about me."
    api->>orch: erase(subject, dry_run=True)
    orch->>prov: lookup(subject)
    prov-->>orch: list of (framework, record_id)
    orch->>adp: preview(records) — parallel
    adp-->>orch: counts (e.g. 14 nodes / 230 embs / 1247 rows)
    orch-->>api: dry-run preview
    api-->>subject: "Here's what will be erased. Confirm?"
    subject->>api: Confirm
    api->>orch: erase(subject, dry_run=False)

    alt happy path
        orch->>adp: erase(records) — parallel
        adp-->>orch: ok per framework
        orch->>prov: purge(subject)
        prov-->>orch: ok
        orch->>sign: sign(manifest)
        sign-->>orch: receipt.json (Ed25519)
        orch-->>api: receipt
        api-->>subject: "Done. Here is your deletion receipt."
        subject->>reg: present receipt.json (as proof)
        reg->>reg: vismaran verify receipt.json<br/>signature ok · hashes ok → OK<br/>tampered any field → FAIL
    else adapter failure (fail-loud, no partial commit)
        orch->>adp: erase(records) — parallel
        adp-->>orch: ok / FAILED<br/>(e.g. pgvector unreachable)
        orch->>orch: detect partial failure
        Note over orch: NO receipt signed.<br/>Operation marked in_progress in audit log.<br/>Idempotent retry resumes from provenance state.
        orch-->>api: PartialErasureError(detail)
        api-->>subject: "Erasure incomplete. Retried automatically. Operator notified."
    end
